# CI / Deployment

- **Build and deploy only via GitHub Actions.** Do not run `pnpm run build`, `deploy.sh`, or `pnpm run deploy` locally.
- To build/deploy: push to `master` and check Actions; or manually trigger CI or Deploy workflow.
- CI: builds plugin, archive, landing, bot; checks API + Telegram connectivity.
- See `AGENTS.md` and `telegram-bot/DEPLOYMENT.md` for details.
